content: I need someone to respond to me in one of the texting channels, but I haven’t heard back from anyone.

Hi <@454416840798502933> I saw you posted a message in https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1266829704204386334. Text team is a different team and has separate on-boarding from Online Engagement. Attend a Text tranfing to join the text team. There is a training on Thursday. After that you will be added to the text team.
I’m just confused bcuz the mod that posted about the text team training said sorry if we missed the beginning of the training this evening, when it wasn’t for texting. It was for online engagement.

I apologize for the confusion. Online engagement is also a great team if you want to do something right away. I appreciate you are intereste in texting, so I hope you can make time for that on Thursday.
No worries! I did the online engagement training and I’m gonna do the texting training on Thursday.
